('accessibility-feature-market-value-uplift-framing', '02', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '[]', 'Backward mining ATTEMPTED: the source PDF (hosted on regjeringen.no) returned HTTP 403 Forbidden on every fetch attempt (WebFetch and direct curl with a browser User-Agent). Unlike the KfW and Socialstyrelsen leads, no alternate mirror was found via web search. DEFERRED pending a working access path. Forward mining: no DOI, no connector — DEFERRED.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20T00:03:51Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch4-pdf', 'source_pdf_403_forbidden'),
('wayfinding-dementia-spatial-design', 'WDS-22', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '[]', 'Backward mining PARTIALLY attempted: fetched and full-text-extracted the main Socialstyrelsen dementia guideline PDF (234K chars, 6 reference sections read in full) — all references are administrative/clinical/economic (care quality metrics, drug cost-effectiveness, demographic registries), not housing-design-specific. The housing-specific evidence base is understood to live in the separate ''Kunskapsunderlag'' (knowledge-base) annex PDF, which returned an HTML redirect/error page rather than PDF content on every fetch attempt (both via WebFetch and direct curl). DEFERRED pending access to that specific annex. Forward mining: no DOI, no connector — DEFERRED.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20T00:03:51Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch4-pdf', 'swedish_annex_pdf_blocked'),
('mental-health-built-environment', 'MHB-28', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '[]', 'Resolved: this is a review of a real book (van Mierlo/Bovenberg/Voskes/Mulder 2013, ''Werkboek HIC'') which is the actual citable source — inserted as REF-00844/MHB-34. The review page itself has no further bibliography.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20T00:38:19Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch6-redo', NULL),
