('cognitive-wayfinding-design', 'CWD-23', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '[]', 'Backward mining PARTIALLY attempted: fetched and full-text-extracted the main Socialstyrelsen dementia guideline PDF (234K chars, 6 reference sections read in full) — all references are administrative/clinical/economic (care quality metrics, drug cost-effectiveness, demographic registries), not housing-design-specific. The housing-specific evidence base is understood to live in the separate ''Kunskapsunderlag'' (knowledge-base) annex PDF, which returned an HTML redirect/error page rather than PDF content on every fetch attempt (both via WebFetch and direct curl). DEFERRED pending access to that specific annex. Forward mining: no DOI, no connector — DEFERRED.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20T00:03:51Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch4-pdf', 'swedish_annex_pdf_blocked'),
