('deaf-spatial-design', 'DSD-13', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '[]', 'note.com blog post fetched and fully read: names Gallaudet University (2005, DeafSpace concept origin), two researchers, and a related organizational credit (Window Research Institute). No formal academic bibliography. NULL RESULT — attempted and complete, not deferred.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20T00:38:19Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch6-redo', NULL),
('wayfinding-dementia-spatial-design', 'WDS-17', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '[]', 'Backward mining ATTEMPTED and COMPLETE: fetched and full-text-extracted the GuiaSalud Alzheimer/dementia clinical guideline PDF (658K chars). This is a general clinical guideline (diagnosis, pharmacology, caregiver support, care coordination) — searched for built-environment/housing-design content (''vivienda'', ''domicilio'', ''hogar'', ''entorno físico'', ''arquitect''); all matches were about care LOCATION (home vs hospital vs institution), not architectural/spatial design. No built-environment-relevant citations found. NULL RESULT, not a deferral — this source''s citation network does not contain evidence relevant to this slug. Forward mining: no DOI, no connector — DEFERRED.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20 00:04', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch4-pdf', NULL),
('accessible-design-economics-cost-premium', 'ECP-03', NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '["ECP-13","ECP-14","ECP-15"]', 'Backward mining COMPLETED: fetched the full KfW/IWU evaluation PDF directly (sanitaerwirtschaft.de mirror; pypdf/pdfminer text extraction after fixing a broken cryptography/cffi binding in the sandbox), located the real Literaturverzeichnis, and extracted genuine citations. 4 relevant sources inserted (REF-00834..00837): Hackmann/Schüssler/Schmutz 2014 age-appropriate housing-adaptation potential analysis, Prognos 2014 predecessor KfW programme evaluation, Gerste 2015 domestic-falls cost-benefit, Edinger/Lerch/Lentze 2007 ''Barrierearm'' concept paper. Many other bibliography entries (burglary victimology, general demographics, labor market) were excluded as out of scope per the relevance filter. Forward mining: no DOI/ISBN, no citation-graph connector for this grey-literature report — DEFERRED.', '2026-07-19T23:46:41Z', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch1', '2026-07-20 00:03', 'session_2026-07-19-citation-mining-nonenglish-batch4-pdf', NULL),
